This server requires node.js, connectjs and db-mysql:


Get node 0.4.12 from here: http://nodejs.org/#download

Then install connect (http://senchalabs.github.com/connect/) by running:
> npm install connect

Then install db-mysql (http://nodejsdb.org/db-mysql/):
NOTE: this requires the mysql connector. if you don't have this, download http://dev.mysql.com/downloads/connector/c/#downloads
> npm install db-mysql